2006-07-23 Bart Hakvoort <hakvoort@cvs.gnome.org>

	* include/FileSystem.h,
	  include/GParted_Core.h,
	  src/FileSystem.cc,
	  src/GParted_Core.cc,
	  src/ext2.cc,
	  src/ext3.cc,
