2005-12-30 Bart Hakvoort <hakvoort@cvs.gnome.org>

	* include/Win_GParted.h,
	  src/Win_GParted.cc: replaced deprecated OptionMenu with ComboBox.
	  also fixed some issues which arised when no devices were detected.

